title: Angry
lastfmSummary: "Angry" is a song by British rock band the Rolling Stones, which serves as the lead single from their upcoming studio album Hackney Diamonds. Released on 6 September 2023, it is the first new original music from the band in three years (following the non-album single "Living in a Ghost Town" in 2020), whilst Hackney Diamonds is their first full-length release of new original music in eighteen years (following A Bigger Bang in 2005).
